# per-developer local settings — must never be committed
# (contains absolute paths / OS username / local command history)
# **/ 付き: ケース dir 配下も対象(arrange.localSettings が実行中だけ生成するファイルの取りこぼし防止)
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# python bytecode (compiled paths embed the local username)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# transient run artifacts (kept locally, not committed)
cases/_*/
# raw headless output
**/result.json
results/**
**/PROOF.txt
**/CONTROL.txt
**/CURLED.txt
**/inside.txt
**/PWNED
cases/*/sub/
*.err
hc.err

# SDK harness deps (run `npm install` inside harness/sdk to restore)
harness/sdk/node_modules/

# interactive modality の staged 状態(prepare〜judge の間だけ存在する一時ファイル)
**/results/.staged.json

# network probe artifacts
**/NETMARKER.txt
**/NETMARKER2.txt
**/nettest_*.out
**/nettest.out
**/nettest2.out
# hook の実行証跡(observe.evidenceFile)。ハーネスが毎回掃除するが手動実行の残骸を拾わない
**/hook-ran.marker
**/OTHER.txt
# S2-f / S2-m の witness / 対照ファイル(手動実行の残骸を拾わない)
**/f-selfprotect-wit.txt
**/f-selfprotect-local-wit.txt
**/f-selfprotect-sub-wit.txt
**/m-selfprotect-wit.txt
**/.claude/other.txt
# probes[].arrange.setup が作る入れ子 fixture(ハーネスが掃除するが手動実行の残骸を拾わない)
cases/*/*/sub/

.DS_Store